data.description: Your wait is over for the perfect magnificent floor plan within your budget!  You will transcend upon the grand entry way, inviting you to the homey greatroom, breakfast and kitchen open space for entertaining.  The master is tucked away privately from the 2nd and 3rd bedroom.  This model offers space for a 1/2 bath in addition to the two full baths.  The large utility/laundry room is a dream.  OH and don't forget the covered deck off the rear which is overlooked by the greatroom.  Display is open from noon-4 pm Wed thru Sunday.  Stop in and pick out one of the newly opened large lots in the new and final phase at Providence! Price shown is base price, the as built price of this display and the options added is $333,351. Price breakdown is attached.
